        <p><strong>33 kgs of CO<sub>2</sub> saved monthly</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 suggestions-col">
      <img class="suggestions-image" src="images/clothes-hanger.png">
      <div class="suggestions-text">
        <h3>Purchase consignment clothing</h3>
        <p>For buying second-hand or consignment for one out of every two clothing purchases:</p>
