      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 suggestions-col">
      <img class="suggestions-image" src="images/car-sharing.png">
      <div class="suggestions-text">
        <h3>Carpool Wednesday Wheels</h3>
        <p>By carpooling with just one other person on Wednesdays</p>
        <p><strong>108 kgs of CO<sub>2</sub> saved monthly</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 suggestions-col">
