      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 suggestions-col">
      <img class="suggestions-image" src="images/fuel.png">
      <div class="suggestions-text">
        <h3>Improve your fuel economy</h3>
        <p>For every 5 km/L you improve the fuel economy of your car:</p>
        <p><strong>75 kgs of CO<sub>2</sub> saved monthly</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 suggestions-col">
      <img class="suggestions-image" src="images/tire-inflation.png">
      <div class="suggestions-text">
        <h3>Keep inflated</h3>
        <p>By keeping your car tires properly inflated:</p>
        <p><strong>33 kgs of CO<sub>2</sub> saved monthly</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


